{"tid":1838410,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【心戰】要阻止大陸人來港求醫，除咗物理封關，心理上都極其重要","createTime":"2020-01-24T04:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T06:15:35.000Z","uid":205733,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"07bd803b7649961e66417d3301ef2514f61e482b","tid":1838410,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:14:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>點解大陸病人會落來香港醫病<br />\n係因爲 來香港生存機會》》大陸生存機會<br />\n呀媽係女人既野。<br />\n重點來喇</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁如果佢地覺得 來香港生存機會 等於/細過 大陸生存機會 會點<br />\n</span></span></strong> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">起碼唔會來，甚至離開香港返大陸/去其他國家</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><br />\n- 如果有人善意提醒，原來到香港其實無大陸咁安全？<br />\n- 如果有消息指大陸病人會一車車唔知車去邊呢？<br />\n- 如果去到醫院求診，會唔會安全呢？<br />\n<br />\n本是同根生，提醒下佢地提防<br />\n記住唔好過分解讀，最緊要唔好做犯法野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"004320a03a782cd20c2db8b55fab17fe92e5123d","tid":1838410,"uid":205733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:15:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和勇合一同抗疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"5819536c45f6e6bc397bee867d4e770d09406618","tid":1838410,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"004320a03a782cd20c2db8b55fab17fe92e5123d","tid":1838410,"uid":205733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:15:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和勇合一同抗疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:16:26.000Z","msg":"明既就會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /